### cafe-notification-daemon 1.24.1

  * tx: sync with transifex
  * build: silent build warnings for distcheck
  * Filter-out img elements from notification body
  * The body of a notification may also contain hyperlinks
  * build: Remove generated files

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.24.0

  * bump version

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.23.1

  * Translations update
  * migrate from intltools to gettext
  * Use gresource for cafe-notification-properties.ui
  * Use WARN_CFLAGS which are only set with --enable-compiler-warnings
  * Fix decoding the hints dictionary.
  * cafe-notification-properties: initialize do-not-disturb checkbox
  * cafe-notification-properties: Add do-not-disturb checkbox
  * daemon.c: check for do-not-disturb and skip notification
  * add do-not-disturb setting

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.23.0

  * Translations update
  * Remove trailing whitespaces
  * Change url project's website
  * [ci] Add cppcheck html report
  * [ci] Enable Clang Static Analyzer

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.22.0

  * Translations update
  * initial travis-CI support
  * disable deprecation warnings for distcheck
  * Avoid compile warning for g_type_class_add_private

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.21.0

  * Translations update
  * Drop dbus-glib dependence
  * Use GVariant
  * Migrate from dbus-glib to GDBus
  * Add signals, remove annotation from xml file
  * Use gdbus generate files
  * Fix some gdk deprecations
  * src/daemon/daemon.c: Replace deprecated gvfs-open call by "gio open" from libglib2.0-bin.

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.20.0

  * Translations update
  * require CTK+ 3.22 and GLib 2.50

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.19.1

  * Translations update
  * WidthOfScreen and HeightOfScreen implementation

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.19.0

  * Translations update
  * ctk 3.22: avoid deprecated gdk_screen_get_monitor... functions:
  * avoid deprecated gdk_screen_get_width/height
  * avoid deprecated gdk_screen_get_n_monitors
  * Fixes high cpu usage with large timeouts
  * unescape URI-encode paths for icon files
  * Restore Polish translation credits from GNOME

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.18.0

  * NEWS: use consistent, project wide, markdown-like formatting
    to make generating release announcements easier
  * Implement action icons support (e.g. playback control icons
    used by media players)
  * Themes: fix some pie countdown issues
  * Translations update

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.16.1

  * Fix markup parsing
  * Translations update

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.16.0

  * Build: use 'm4' dir instead of 'macros' for m4 macros, like
    in other projects
  * Move to CTK+3 (require CTK+ >= 3.14), drop CTK+2 code and
    --with-ctk build option
  * Add support for GNotification
  * Fix escaping of special characters
  * Fix various CTK+ deprecations
  * Translations update

### cafe-notification-daemon 1.14.1

