### cafe-notification-daemon 1.14.0

  * Drop CafeConf migration script
  * CTK+3: explicitly wrap notification text at 50 characters
  * CTK+3: stop reversing fg/bg colors in slider theme (use colors
    from current CTK+ theme as is)
  * CTK+3: some more fixes for slider theme
  * CTK+3: some deprecation fixes
  * Translations update
  * Add Changelog generation

